326
00:14:00,670 --> 00:14:01,550
Giving up.

327
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:02,870
Why?

328
00:14:04,530 --> 00:14:06,410
Many people get bullied from a young age.

329
00:14:06,580 --> 00:14:08,150
They grow up in harsh environments,

330
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:09,790
but they still live just fine.

331
00:14:10,150 --> 00:14:11,510
So you mean

332
00:14:11,530 --> 00:14:13,770
Xiao Nannan should just put up with it?

333
