I didn't say that.

334
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:17,600
I just experienced more than her.

335
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:19,070
I know that many things

336
00:14:19,100 --> 00:14:20,230
can't be fixed

337
00:14:21,400 --> 00:14:22,430
by the law,

338
00:14:23,250 --> 00:14:24,580
sometimes it's better to just rely on yourself.

339
