you can't be so fragile.

341
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:31,640
You think Xiao Nannan is fragile?

342
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:33,120
I think so.

343
00:14:34,250 --> 00:14:36,480
I've experienced more than her since I was a kid.

344
00:14:36,790 --> 00:14:38,550
I'm still living just fine.

345
00:14:39,390 --> 00:14:40,200
Qiu,

346
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:43,240
I can't agree with you.

347
00:14:43,630 --> 00:14:45,120
It's because so many people

348
00:14:45,120 --> 00:14:45,840
think like you do

349
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:48,030
