397
00:16:24,550 --> 00:16:26,590
You and Xiao Nannan were high school classmates, right?

398
00:16:26,740 --> 00:16:29,500
Xiao Nannan? That rich girl?

399
00:16:26,830 --> 00:16:29,530
[School Bullying Perpetrator: Zhang Xiaolian]

400
00:16:29,750 --> 00:16:31,030
I must remind you that

