410
00:16:47,670 --> 00:16:48,710
Comfort her feelings?

411
00:16:48,730 --> 00:16:49,960
Who will comfort me?

412
00:16:50,010 --> 00:16:52,290
We just gave her a nickname

413
00:16:52,630 --> 00:16:53,820
and joked around a little;

414
00:16:54,750 --> 00:16:56,320
