437
00:17:34,070 --> 00:17:34,620
Get lost!

438
00:17:38,720 --> 00:17:39,680
You're being unreasonable.

439
00:17:42,440 --> 00:17:44,360
Apologize? No way.

440
00:18:16,590 --> 00:18:17,580
Hello, Xiao Nannan.

441
00:18:18,430 --> 00:18:19,200
Please have a seat.

442
00:18:25,050 --> 00:18:26,730
