443
00:18:27,110 --> 00:18:27,720
Sure.

444
00:18:27,750 --> 00:18:28,900
Thank you, Ms. Qiu.

445
00:18:29,030 --> 00:18:29,670
You're welcome.

446
00:18:35,590 --> 00:18:36,640
I invited you here today

447
00:18:36,640 --> 00:18:38,310
