they were just kids back then,

454
00:19:00,550 --> 00:19:02,750
and all they did was make a few casual jokes.

455
00:19:03,600 --> 00:19:04,430
Besides,

456
00:19:05,050 --> 00:19:06,860
your family is better off than theirs,

457
00:19:07,410 --> 00:19:08,820
so it was inevitable that

458
00:19:09,280 --> 00:19:11,000
they held some resentment toward you.

459
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:13,070
