00:23:43,610 --> 00:23:44,980
Logically speaking,

565
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:48,200
the boss of Minghai Group

566
00:23:48,830 --> 00:23:50,300
is a senior official at the department level.

567
00:23:50,650 --> 00:23:52,680
How could he possibly care about a private enterprise owner?

568
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:54,160
It's because you

569
00:23:54,310 --> 00:23:55,590
did such a solid job in the first trial

570
00:23:55,590 --> 00:23:57,030
and gathered evidence so thoroughly.

571
00:23:57,030 --> 00:23:57,670
They knew that

572
00:23:57,700 --> 00:23:59,270
even if the case went to the second trial,

573
00:23:59,270 --> 00:24:00,160
they'd still lose.

574
00:24:00,390 --> 00:24:01,910
That's why he put on a show.

575
00:24:03,350 --> 00:24:05,270
Sun Mingshan isn't stupid.

576
00:24:05,270 --> 00:24:06,550
He knows what Minghai Group is afraid of.

577
00:24:07,830 --> 00:24:08,720
So,

578
00:24:08,880 --> 00:24:10,560
no matter how Minghai Group's attitude changes,

579
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:12,270
the core demand of Mingshan Group won't change.

580
00:24:12,270 --> 00:24:13,660
They just want Minghai Group to pay back the money.

581
00:24:13,790 --> 00:24:14,680
That's the point.

582
00:24:22,140 --> 00:24:24,620
[Mr. Sun]

583
00:24:24,980 --> 00:24:28,220
Meeting with Minghai Group behind my back, you really know how to play the game.

584
00:24:30,270 --> 00:24:32,510
Hello, Mr. Sun. I'm Chen Shuo.

585
00:24:33,030 --> 00:24:34,200
Regarding Minghai Group's situation,

586
00:24:34,200 --> 00:24:36,340
the company I hired has almost finished the investigation.

587
00:24:36,750 --> 00:24:38,610
They've bought a piece of land

588
00:24:38,630 --> 00:24:39,590
in Pingling.

589
00:24:39,840 --> 00:24:41,020
The internal sources say

590
00:24:41,050 --> 00:24:42,130
it's for building dormitories,

591
00:24:42,160 --> 00:24:44,550
but the specific purpose isn't important.

592
00:24:44,720 --> 00:24:45,790
What matters is that

593
00:24:45,830 --> 00:24:46,720
this land

594
00:24:47,050 --> 00:24:48,720
hasn't been seized yet,

595
00:24:48,750 --> 00:24:49,790
and its property value

596
00:24:49,790 --> 00:24:51,830
is enough to cover most of the debt.

597
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:53,050
Given the situation,

598
00:24:53,400 --> 00:24:55,360
do you think we should provide this information to the court as soon as possible?

599
00:24:55,940 --> 00:24:57,210
You really found it.

600
00:24:57,790 --> 00:24:58,790
Go ahead and provide it.

601
00:24:59,270 --> 00:25:00,160
They

602
00:25:00,190 --> 00:25:01,990
won't give up until they're in deep trouble.

603
00:25:02,180 --> 00:25:04,380
If they don't actively enforce the judgment,

604
00:25:04,550 --> 00:25:06,030
we'll apply for enforcement ourselves.

605
00:25:07,070 --> 00:25:08,550
I'll provide it to the court then.

606
00:25:08,990 --> 00:25:10,320
Also, Mr. Sun,

607
00:25:10,430 --> 00:25:11,600
there's one important point,

608
00:25:11,960 --> 00:25:14,670
as mentioned

609
00:25:14,790 --> 00:25:15,710
in our previous agency agreement,

610
00:25:16,030 --> 00:25:16,830
we both

611
00:25:16,830 --> 00:25:18,590
need to set up a joint account

612
00:25:18,790 --> 00:25:20,680
to collect payments

613
00:25:20,710 --> 00:25:21,790
and enforcement funds.

614
00:25:21,790 --> 00:25:23,310
Now that enforcement is about to start,

615
00:25:23,550 --> 00:25:25,750
would it be possible for you to send someone

616
00:25:25,750 --> 00:25:27,140
to coordinate with me on this matter?

617
00:25:27,340 --> 00:25:28,940
Sure. When do you think is okay?

618
00:25:29,520 --> 00:25:30,650
The sooner, the better.

619
00:25:30,680 --> 00:25:32,310
Wait, how about tomorrow?

620
00:25:32,330 --> 00:25:34,120
Okay, I'll send someone there tomorrow.

621
00:25:34,780 --> 00:25:35,670
You go ahead with your work.

622
00:25:35,700 --> 00:25:36,590
I'll wait for you.

623
00:25:40,920 --> 00:25:42,070
If you're ungrateful to me,

624
00:25:42,150 --> 00:25:43,540
don't blame me for being harsh with you.

625
00:25:49,070 --> 00:25:49,640
Mr. Sun,

626
00:25:50,900 --> 00:25:53,010
we're in negotiations with Minghai Group right now.

627
00:25:53,270 --> 00:25:55,510
Is it a good time to bring up enforcement?

628
00:25:55,610 --> 00:25:56,720
What's wrong with that?

629
00:25:59,790 --> 00:26:01,310
We're negotiating with them,

630
00:26:01,350 --> 00:26:03,550
but they keep dragging things out;

631
00:26:03,920 --> 00:26:05,400
they just don't want to pay.

632
00:26:05,750 --> 00:26:07,400
As long as the deal isn't done,

633
00:26:08,160 --> 00:26:09,160
we should push for enforcement.

634
00:26:09,600 --> 00:26:10,970
We should seize

635
00:26:11,000 --> 00:26:12,030
as many assets as possible.

636
00:26:13,200 --> 00:26:14,590
The more we enforce,

637
00:26:15,150 --> 00:26:17,260
the stronger our position in negotiations.

638
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:21,550
Does Mr. Chen know about the negotiations?

639
00:26:22,690 --> 00:26:24,140
We can't let him know.

640
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:25,120
By the way,

641
00:26:25,720 --> 00:26:27,540
make sure everyone who knows about this

642
00:26:27,690 --> 00:26:28,690
keeps it strictly confidential.

643
00:26:28,740 --> 00:26:30,220
We absolutely cannot let Mr. Chen

644
00:26:30,290 --> 00:26:31,540
hear a word of it.

645
00:26:34,290 --> 00:26:35,090
Come in.

646
00:26:36,280 --> 00:26:37,320
Mr. Han, are you looking for me?

647
00:26:37,710 --> 00:26:39,990
I've been waiting for you.

648
00:26:41,030 --> 00:26:42,160
Sit down.

649
00:26:42,240 --> 00:26:43,000
The door is also closed.

650
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:43,680
Sit down.

651
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:44,240
Why so serious?

652
00:26:44,240 --> 00:26:45,440
What's going on?

653
00:26:46,050 --> 00:26:48,660
I've received confirmed news—

654
00:26:49,160 --> 00:26:51,810
Mingshan Group and Minghai Group are in talks.

655
00:26:53,160 --> 00:26:54,270
That's a bit underhanded.

656
00:26:54,510 --> 00:26:56,230
I had a feeling before.

657
00:26:57,640 --> 00:26:59,010
Whenever something like this happens,

658
00:26:59,240 --> 00:27:01,080
it's always a given that

659
00:27:01,160 --> 00:27:02,920
the client will betray their lawyer.

660
00:27:04,030 --> 00:27:05,070
But it's a bit strange.

661
00:27:05,070 --> 00:27:06,470
You said they are negotiating,

662
00:27:07,960 --> 00:27:09,240
but I just called Sun Mingshan

663
00:27:09,240 --> 00:27:10,560
on the way here,

664
00:27:10,920 --> 00:27:11,830
and he was urging me

665
00:27:11,830 --> 00:27:13,480
to hurry up with the enforcement.

666
00:27:13,590 --> 00:27:14,350
Enforcement?

667
00:27:14,350 --> 00:27:15,380
Yes, Sun Mingshan said that.

668
00:27:21,160 --> 00:27:24,160
That means their negotiations didn't succeed.

669
00:27:24,780 --> 00:27:25,930
So what if they didn't succeed?

670
00:27:26,120 --> 00:27:26,990
If they didn't succeed,

671
00:27:28,200 --> 00:27:30,000
they'll use the lawyer

672
00:27:30,240 --> 00:27:31,590
to push for enforcement,

673
00:27:31,590 --> 00:27:34,030
and then when they go back to the negotiating table,

674
00:27:34,030 --> 00:27:36,060
Mingshan Group will have a stronger position,

675
00:27:36,080 --> 00:27:36,830
right?

676
00:27:42,050 --> 00:27:43,620
I didn't think of that.

677
00:27:44,380 --> 00:27:45,380
How about this, Mr. Han?

678
00:27:45,680 --> 00:27:46,790
I have to call you Mentor.

679
00:27:46,790 --> 00:27:48,120
I'll pay my respects as your disciple.

680
00:27:48,140 --> 00:27:49,110
Okay? Look.

681
00:27:49,110 --> 00:27:49,750
Fine.

682
00:27:49,750 --> 00:27:50,760
You're amazing.

683
00:27:51,470 --> 00:27:53,080
Flatter me after we get the money.

684
00:27:55,160 --> 00:27:55,880
Fine.

685
00:27:55,880 --> 00:27:59,000
Let's get on with the enforcement right away.

686
00:28:00,210 --> 00:28:01,180
Don't be greedy.

687
00:28:01,620 --> 00:28:03,620
As their assets are seized, we make a withdrawal.

688
00:28:03,820 --> 00:28:06,340
Then we'll go straight to Mingshan Group for negotiations

689
00:28:06,390 --> 00:28:08,350
and cut our losses as soon as possible, understand?

690
00:28:08,750 --> 00:28:09,800
Okay, I got it.

691
00:28:10,340 --> 00:28:11,350
I told Sun Mingshan

692
00:28:11,350 --> 00:28:13,590
to build the joint account as soon as possible.

693
00:28:13,590 --> 00:28:14,870
He's sending someone over tomorrow,

694
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:16,030
and we'll go to the bank together.

695
00:28:16,830 --> 00:28:18,510
Wait, building a joint account?

696
00:28:18,510 --> 00:28:20,030
If they disagree,

697
00:28:20,030 --> 00:28:21,000
we can't come up with the money,

698
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:22,660
then we'll have done all this for nothing.

699
00:28:22,690 --> 00:28:24,940
You need to make sure who's going to set up the account

700
00:28:25,400 --> 00:28:27,060
and how they're going to do it.

701
00:28:37,580 --> 00:28:38,250
Chen Shuo,

702
00:28:38,720 --> 00:28:39,680
you can't do this.

703
00:28:39,950 --> 00:28:41,110
What did I do?

704
00:28:41,510 --> 00:28:43,590
It's too risky to get caught.

705
00:28:45,090 --> 00:28:46,720
Mr. Han, you're worrying too much.

706
00:28:47,110 --> 00:28:48,270
I am a lawyer.

707
00:28:48,270 --> 00:28:50,240
I won't do anything illegal.

708
00:28:50,480 --> 00:28:51,180
Also,

709
00:28:51,200 --> 00:28:52,550
as long as they fulfill the agreement,

710
00:28:52,550 --> 00:28:53,580
the joint account

711
00:28:53,730 --> 00:28:55,080
is just an account.

712
00:28:56,230 --> 00:28:57,080
Brother,

713
00:28:57,100 --> 00:28:58,530
listen to me.

714
00:28:59,430 --> 00:29:02,800
Have you ever heard of any lawyer making eight to ten million

715
00:29:02,830 --> 00:29:04,570
just from the first trial?

716
00:29:05,210 --> 00:29:07,140
From the very beginning, I knew that

717
00:29:07,170 --> 00:29:09,650
the bid from Mingshan Group was just a gimmick,

718
00:29:09,860 --> 00:29:12,340
designed to lure lawyers in.

719
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:15,950
Brother, let's lower the price.

720
00:29:16,360 --> 00:29:18,270
Let's just ask for one million,

721
00:29:18,640 --> 00:29:20,050
and this matter can still be negotiated,

722
00:29:20,070 --> 00:29:20,990
don't you think?

723
00:29:21,090 --> 00:29:22,490
I can earn 8 million,

724
00:29:22,730 --> 00:29:24,030
but I should settle for 1 million?

725
00:29:24,180 --> 00:29:25,980
No wonder you're young.

726
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:28,000
As the saying goes,

727
00:29:28,130 --> 00:29:30,570
"A bird in the hand is worth more than two in the bush."

728
00:29:30,670 --> 00:29:32,840
What you can get is real money;

729
00:29:32,890 --> 00:29:33,910
what you can't get

730
00:29:33,940 --> 00:29:35,130
is just numbers on paper.

731
00:29:35,160 --> 00:29:36,830
Mr. Han,

732
00:29:36,830 --> 00:29:38,110
I'm just following the agreement on this.

733
00:29:38,270 --> 00:29:39,400
I just want what I deserve.

734
00:29:39,400 --> 00:29:40,400
If you're worried,

735
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:42,440
you can report it to the firm

736
00:29:42,470 --> 00:29:44,470
and see what's the firm's decision.

737
00:29:45,010 --> 00:29:47,580
Wait, why should I report it?

738
00:29:48,160 --> 00:29:49,030
The more you earn,

739
00:29:49,030 --> 00:29:51,040
the more I get too, right?

740
00:29:51,060 --> 00:29:52,610
There you go, brother.

741
00:29:52,910 --> 00:29:54,480
Don't worry. I'll let you know

742
00:29:54,510 --> 00:29:55,960
if there's any progress on my end, okay?

743
00:29:56,680 --> 00:29:57,510
-Don't worry.
-Okay.

744
00:29:57,510 --> 00:29:58,270
Alright.

745
00:30:11,960 --> 00:30:12,880
Ms. Xiao,

746
00:30:13,640 --> 00:30:15,450
your phone is off,

747
00:30:15,470 --> 00:30:17,610
so I had no choice but to apologize this way.

748
00:30:17,790 --> 00:30:20,270
I didn't mean to leak your phone number.

749
00:30:20,330 --> 00:30:22,330
It was my own careless handling.

750
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:24,160
This has nothing to do with Ms. Qiu.

751
00:30:24,610 --> 00:30:25,680
I'm truly sorry.

752
00:30:26,460 --> 00:30:28,020
What is it?

753
00:30:29,220 --> 00:30:30,460
Your coffee is good.

754
00:30:31,500 --> 00:30:32,660
Let's get down to business.

755
00:30:33,890 --> 00:30:35,330
My uncle and younger uncle

756
00:30:36,090 --> 00:30:37,680
have basically won over

757
00:30:37,700 --> 00:30:38,390
Mr. Ma and Mr. Yang.

758
00:30:38,420 --> 00:30:39,220
It's too quick.

759
00:30:40,750 --> 00:30:42,790
What about Lan? You still can't contact her?

760
00:30:42,840 --> 00:30:44,160
She's in the country,

761
00:30:44,480 --> 00:30:45,790
but when I went to her place,

762
00:30:46,400 --> 00:30:47,290
she wouldn't see me.

763
00:30:47,860 --> 00:30:48,970
Do you have any idea?

764
00:30:50,510 --> 00:30:51,720
How would I know?

765
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:55,440
Let me think about it.

766
00:31:00,710 --> 00:31:03,080
Hao Lei, let me ask you a question.

767
00:31:03,940 --> 00:31:05,660
Even if you don't become the president,

768
00:31:05,830 --> 00:31:06,930
you're still a major shareholder.

769
00:31:07,130 --> 00:31:08,500
You're not short on money,

770
00:31:08,790 --> 00:31:10,790
so why fight with your uncle and younger uncle?

771
00:31:11,350 --> 00:31:12,440
You lawyers

772
00:31:12,870 --> 00:31:14,590
can make money

773
00:31:14,590 --> 00:31:15,550
taking on regular cases too.

774
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:17,550
Why go after debts,

775
00:31:17,650 --> 00:31:19,090
throwing yourself under someone's car wheels

776
00:31:19,260 --> 00:31:20,700
or apologizing to clients in the middle of the night?

777
00:31:21,150 --> 00:31:22,260
What's in it for you?

778
00:31:22,280 --> 00:31:23,820
This is called a sense of accomplishment.

779
00:31:23,850 --> 00:31:24,850
Do you understand?

780
00:31:26,340 --> 00:31:27,340
A sense of accomplishment?

781
00:31:28,450 --> 00:31:30,490
Did your sense of accomplishment come from

782
00:31:30,550 --> 00:31:32,000
crawling under car wheels

783
00:31:32,000 --> 00:31:32,730
or playing mind games with loan sharks?

784
00:31:32,750 --> 00:31:33,750
Why didn't I have a sense of accomplishment?

785
00:31:34,010 --> 00:31:35,680
I think I'm pretty impressive.

786
00:31:38,390 --> 00:31:40,390
I used to feel like I had everything,

787
00:31:41,070 --> 00:31:42,730
but in reality, I have nothing.

788
00:31:43,330 --> 00:31:44,770
I have nothing now.

789
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:47,400
But I still have to hold on to something.

790
00:31:47,960 --> 00:31:49,200
Aren't you the same?

791
00:31:49,620 --> 00:31:50,890
So I think

792
00:31:51,380 --> 00:31:52,870
we are quite alike.

793
00:31:53,200 --> 00:31:55,410
Enough. Stop pretending to be close.

794
00:31:56,350 --> 00:31:57,750
You tricked me into working for you.

795
00:31:57,880 --> 00:31:58,830
Let's get down to business.

796
00:31:59,380 --> 00:32:01,650
You can only rely on Lan now.

797
00:32:01,750 --> 00:32:02,640
What should you do?

798
00:32:02,720 --> 00:32:03,770
You like sense of accomplishment,

799
00:32:04,810 --> 00:32:05,680
so you go ask her out.

800
00:32:07,140 --> 00:32:07,730
I...

801
00:32:08,880 --> 00:32:09,750
I'll leave it to you.

802
00:32:14,810 --> 00:32:17,200
Okay, I owe you.

803
00:32:23,400 --> 00:32:25,510
Mentor, this is Miss Dong from the Mingshan Group.

804
00:32:25,510 --> 00:32:26,310
This is my mentor.

805
00:32:26,640 --> 00:32:27,440
Mr. Chen.

806
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:29,640
I'm Dong Yao, just call me Dong.

807
00:32:29,640 --> 00:32:30,720
No, I'll call you Miss Dong.

808
00:32:30,740 --> 00:32:31,400
Hello.

809
00:32:31,400 --> 00:32:31,880
Hello.

810
00:32:31,910 --> 00:32:32,470
I'm sorry

811
00:32:32,470 --> 00:32:33,960
to trouble you with the trip today.

812
00:32:33,960 --> 00:32:34,630
It's okay.

813
00:32:35,310 --> 00:32:36,610
Do you have your ID and authorization letter with you?

814
00:32:36,630 --> 00:32:37,390
Yes.

815
00:32:37,510 --> 00:32:37,970
Okay.

816
00:32:38,270 --> 00:32:40,120
Mentor, I'll take care of the errand.

817
00:32:41,030 --> 00:32:41,830
Errand?

818
00:32:42,630 --> 00:32:44,150
There are no small matters when it comes to Mingshan Group.

819
00:32:44,200 --> 00:32:45,830
Every task is crucial,

820
00:32:45,830 --> 00:32:47,000
and I must handle it personally.

821
00:32:47,680 --> 00:32:49,030
I've already contacted the bank,

822
00:32:49,030 --> 00:32:50,680
and it won't take much of your time,

823
00:32:50,680 --> 00:32:51,920
and we'll get it done quickly.

824
00:32:51,920 --> 00:32:52,370
Okay.

825
00:32:53,530 --> 00:32:54,210
You go first.

826
00:32:54,590 --> 00:32:55,350
I'll get you a car.

827
00:32:55,350 --> 00:32:56,010
No need.

828
00:32:56,300 --> 00:32:57,950
Work hard. Don't slack off.

829
00:32:59,350 --> 00:33:00,070
Miss Dong,

830
00:33:00,310 --> 00:33:01,070
these are the agreements

831
00:33:01,070 --> 00:33:03,310
required for us

832
00:33:03,310 --> 00:33:04,320
to establish the joint account.

833
00:33:04,340 --> 00:33:06,050
Our firm has already stamped them.

834
00:33:06,110 --> 00:33:07,110
See if there's any problem.

835
00:33:07,110 --> 00:33:08,030
If not,

836
00:33:08,030 --> 00:33:09,790
you can just have the Mingshan seal placed,

837
00:33:09,790 --> 00:33:11,310
and we'll submit them to the bank.

838
00:33:11,480 --> 00:33:12,900
Okay. Mr. Chen, let me take a look.

839
00:33:19,440 --> 00:33:20,240
Miss Dong,

840
00:33:21,030 --> 00:33:23,820
I feel like I've seen you before.

841
00:33:24,870 --> 00:33:27,150
I had dinner once

842
00:33:27,170 --> 00:33:28,280
with Mr. Sun and Mrs. Sun.

843
00:33:28,400 --> 00:33:29,420
Mrs. Sun

844
00:33:29,440 --> 00:33:31,040
left quite a deep impression on me then.

